Before the upgrade of JIRA OnDemand for 5.0.7rc1, the following HTML code would work:
{noformat}
<a href="https://battle.atlassian.net/wiki/">The World of Atlassian (EAP)</a>
{noformat}

Now, it is displayed as plain text on the instances.

Update 149 breaks POP/IMAP connection. Testing the mail servers connection in UI - okay.

Doing test in mail handler will throw error and in the log, every connection will timed out.

{noformat}
@400000004fd5df6e0f850f84 2012-06-11 15:07:00,259 QuartzWorker-0 ERROR ServiceRunner    xxxxxx Mail Handler [atlassian.mail.incoming.mailfetcherservice] xxxxxxx[10112]: Error connecting to host 'pop.gmail.com' as user 'xxxxxx@xxxxxx' via protocol 'pop3s': javax.mail.MessagingException: Connect failed;
@400000004fd5df6e0f85230c   nested exception is:
